'''Thoros''', commonly known as '''Thoros of Myr''', is a recurring character in the [[Season 3|third season]]. He is played by [[Paul Kaye]]. Thoros is a [[Red Priest|red priest]] of the [[Lord of Light]] and a noted warrior.

